    "The following subsections detail the different experiments conducted.",
    "The objective pursued was to thoroughly study (1) which algorithms are able to guarantee better thermal control; (2) which DRL algorithms offer higher robustness to weather conditions for which they have not been trained; (3) the application of sequential learning and its effectiveness to obtain better controllers, and (4) the comfort-consumption trade-off and its influence on the performance of the controllers.",
